data.description: *Two brand new, 2 ton HVAC systems installed!  This home has been LOVED and it really shows!  Dream kitchen and custom cabinets, soft close drawers and granite counters.  Pantry with pull-out drawers with tile flooring.  There is so much storage and counterspace in the kitchen.  Newer refrigerator, kitchen open to dining room with hardwood oaks, perfect for entertaining!    Large den has wood stove and stone accent wall. Laundry room inside.  Both baths renovated.  Sunroom off the kitchen with tile flooring and gas fireplace!  Beautiful views of large backyard, wired workshop can be accessed from carport and sunroom.  Plenty of wood for a wood stove.  2 additional storage sheds.
